FRESHMEAT="patch"
  ESTIMATE="98"
     DESC="patch applies a patch to a file.

GNU version of Larry Wall's program that takes 
diff's output and applies it to an original file 
to generate a modified version of that file.
Normally, the patched versions are put in place of the originals.
Backups can be made.
"
